Package capstone.objects

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Roster
    Each roster correlates to a unique combination of a team and a season along with a list of skaters.
    Season
    A season contains a start year, end year, number of games played, and a list of skater stats.
    Skater
    This class designs a skater object and contains related functions.
    Stats
    ALL STATS ARE PROVIDED BY HOCKEY-REFERENCE.COM Each stat line consists of a unique combination of a skater and a season.
    Team
    This class designs the team object and contains relevant functions.
    User
    Designs the user object and contains relevant functions.
